                            -=} The Bitrig Logo {=-


The Bitrig logo consists of a derrick (somtimes incorrectly refered to as oil
rig) and the word bitrig underlined by a oil pipeline.


COLOR

green (#0d7340) and white (#ffffff)


FONT

The Bitrig logo uses Roboto available at Font Squirrel[1]

[1] http://www.fontsquirrel.com/fonts/roboto
